channel.title: Problems with running my server! [HELP!]

i have some problems with running my server.

then...
it's just like i'm on 127.0.0.1!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! nothing is edited in there, just frustrating!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
plz, if u know how to solve, then tell me!!!
